description:
Jay Will rides up Paramount Mountain on the Peak Talk ski lift with Josh Horowitz to talk all things Tulsa King. Jay (Tyson Mitchell) shares his background in theater training at The Juilliard School, what he’s learned on-set from Sylvester Stallone (Dwight Manfredi), and what it was like meeting Samuel L. Jackson while filming Season 3.
